♪Two stars shine bright,
facing each other from afar♪

563
00:31:16,750 --> 00:31:17,900
My dear daughter,

564
00:31:18,700 --> 00:31:20,180
survive.

565
00:31:21,140 --> 00:31:23,310
You must survive.

566
00:31:27,380 --> 00:31:28,350
Don't go.

567
00:31:32,140 --> 00:31:36,900
♪Broken, yet never destroyed♪

568
00:31:37,620 --> 00:31:42,420
♪The purple star, without regret,
shines on the lake♪

569
00:31:45,310 --> 00:31:46,180
Yu,

570
00:31:46,590 --> 00:31:47,870
I'm not leaving.

571
00:31:48,310 --> 00:31:49,380
If I leave, you're coming with me.

572
00:31:49,380 --> 00:31:50,590
You're pregnant.

573
00:31:50,590 --> 00:31:51,830
Return to Hepu first.

574
00:31:51,830 --> 00:31:53,220
I wonder if the master
and the others are...

575
00:31:53,220 --> 00:31:55,180
They'll be fine.

576
00:31:55,180 --> 00:31:56,660
You must take care of our child.

577
00:31:56,660 --> 00:31:58,220
Yu!

578
00:31:59,790 --> 00:32:00,980
Steward Yan has returned.

579
00:32:00,980 --> 00:32:02,140
He said everyone
in the Yan family had died,

580
00:32:02,140 --> 00:32:03,550
and that the Cui family
owned the pearl farm now.

581
00:32:03,550 --> 00:32:05,270
What should we do, Lady Yan?

582
00:32:06,460 --> 00:32:07,220
Lady Yan!

583
00:32:07,220 --> 00:32:09,110
Are you alright, Lady Yan?

584
00:32:11,180 --> 00:32:15,980
♪Life is just
love, hate, and desire on repeat...♪

585
00:32:17,790 --> 00:32:19,310
Listen up!

586
00:32:19,310 --> 00:32:21,420
This pearl farm
now belongs to the Cui family!

587
00:32:21,420 --> 00:32:23,220
Defy us,

588
00:32:23,700 --> 00:32:25,140
and you'll end up like this!

589
00:32:25,140 --> 00:32:26,070
Do you hear me?

590
00:32:27,540 --> 00:32:30,930
♪Meetings and partings
are beyond our control♪

591
00:32:30,940 --> 00:32:33,940
Lady Yan, why did you do this?

592
00:32:34,380 --> 00:32:35,830
This is the only way

593
00:32:36,870 --> 00:32:39,830
I can bring her into this world safely

594
00:32:40,900 --> 00:32:42,590
and protect her.

595
00:32:44,070 --> 00:32:46,110
I don't want her
to end up a pearl diver.

596
00:32:46,900 --> 00:32:48,590
She was born on the fifth day
of the fifth month.

597
00:32:48,980 --> 00:32:50,420
I'll name her Duanwu.

598
00:32:50,870 --> 00:32:51,830
Please,

599
00:32:52,270 --> 00:32:53,830
promise me you'll take good care of her.

600
00:32:53,830 --> 00:32:55,380
- Rest assured.
- Rest assured.

601
00:32:57,140 --> 00:32:58,310
Duanwu.

602
00:32:58,310 --> 00:32:59,080
Duanwu.

603
00:32:59,090 --> 00:33:03,100
♪New years grow
from withered memories...♪

604
00:33:03,550 --> 00:33:04,270
Your name?

605
00:33:04,870 --> 00:33:07,270
My name is Zhaohua.

606
00:33:09,030 --> 00:33:10,900
Your name? Speak up!

607
00:33:11,750 --> 00:33:14,220
My... My name is Duanwu.

608
00:33:14,250 --> 00:33:20,100
♪Guarding your final light♪

609
00:33:21,980 --> 00:33:26,820
♪A mortal life can be summed up
in just a few fleeting words♪

610
00:33:27,220 --> 00:33:32,050
♪Fierce winds and rushing rain
cannot quench my flame♪

611
00:33:32,660 --> 00:33:37,450
♪Alas, love and hate
will both find their end♪

612
00:33:37,940 --> 00:33:42,700
♪Why count gains and losses
along the way?♪

613
00:33:43,220 --> 00:33:48,020
♪Alas, life always leads to death♪

614
00:33:48,460 --> 00:33:57,220
♪May we meet again someday♪

615
00:34:12,460 --> 00:34:13,420
The pearl...

616
00:34:13,420 --> 00:34:14,350
Duanwu,

617
00:34:14,350 --> 00:34:16,320
I think someone picked up the pearl

618
00:34:16,320 --> 00:34:17,310
Lady Eight gave you!

619
00:34:28,590 --> 00:34:29,180
Let's go.

620
00:34:49,900 --> 00:34:51,270
The ledger has been delivered.

621
00:34:52,420 --> 00:34:54,700
This pearl farm in Hepu
is a den of filth and corruption.

622
00:34:55,660 --> 00:34:56,660
This ledger

623
00:34:57,270 --> 00:34:59,350
should make a fine gift for Prince Ying.

624
00:34:59,350 --> 00:35:01,940
Prince Ying and Prince Tan
are locked in fierce conflict.

625
00:35:02,220 --> 00:35:03,850
If Zhang Jinran could truly expose

626
00:35:03,850 --> 00:35:05,460
Prince Tan's embezzlement
of the tribute pearls,

627
00:35:05,460 --> 00:35:08,590
the Cui family would be doomed.

628
00:35:08,590 --> 00:35:10,140
This is just the beginning.

629
00:35:11,310 --> 00:35:12,870
Did you find the person
I asked you to locate?

630
00:35:13,140 --> 00:35:14,070
Not yet.

631
00:35:16,180 --> 00:35:17,070
Leave two people here

632
00:35:17,790 --> 00:35:18,750
to keep looking.

633
00:35:18,750 --> 00:35:19,420
Understood.

634
00:35:23,420 --> 00:35:24,830
Is the illness acting up again?

635
00:35:32,830 --> 00:35:33,590
It's nothing.

636
00:35:35,660 --> 00:35:36,660
Put it out!

637
00:35:37,790 --> 00:35:39,230
Hurry. Get more people to help!

638
00:35:39,230 --> 00:35:39,540
Yes, sir.

639
00:35:39,540 --> 00:35:40,230
Hurry!

640
00:35:42,060 --> 00:35:43,790
Duanwu didn't start this fire.

641
00:35:43,790 --> 00:35:46,190
The Pearl Tower and the pearl farm
caught fire at the same time.

642
00:35:46,190 --> 00:35:47,710
Someone must have
planned this in advance.

643
00:35:47,710 --> 00:35:48,750
There's more fire over there!

644
00:35:48,750 --> 00:35:49,580
How are the books?

645
00:35:49,580 --> 00:35:50,750
The counting house burned down.

646
00:35:51,150 --> 00:35:53,540
The account books
are probably all destroyed.

647
00:35:53,540 --> 00:35:54,190
Good.

648
00:35:55,790 --> 00:35:56,900
It's better they're burned.

649
00:35:56,900 --> 00:35:58,380
How should we
explain this to the master?

650
00:35:58,980 --> 00:36:01,100
Steward Cui,

651
00:36:01,710 --> 00:36:03,750
Master Shijiu's ship is about to dock.

652
00:36:03,750 --> 00:36:04,750
What's she doing here?

653
00:36:04,750 --> 00:36:06,190
Could she be here for her dowry?

654
00:36:06,710 --> 00:36:08,310
That girl

655
00:36:08,310 --> 00:36:10,710
always dresses like a man.

656
00:36:11,060 --> 00:36:12,750
I doubt she's here for a dowry.

657
00:36:13,710 --> 00:36:15,350
She's here to deal with me!

658
00:36:15,500 --> 00:36:18,980
[Cui]

659
00:36:18,980 --> 00:36:21,100
This year, the farm
produced 43 Qizhen pearls

660
00:36:21,100 --> 00:36:22,100
and 2.3 sheng of small pearls.

661
00:36:22,100 --> 00:36:24,100
Among the tribute pearls, there are
ten Qizhen and nine Babao pearls.

662
00:36:24,100 --> 00:36:25,190
We also have 5.3 sheng of smooth pearls

663
00:36:25,190 --> 00:36:26,460
and 11.2 sheng of rolling pearls.

664
00:36:26,460 --> 00:36:27,830
- Altogether...
- I recall

665
00:36:28,350 --> 00:36:30,350
that last year, we had 56 Qizhen pearls

666
00:36:30,350 --> 00:36:31,750
and three sheng of small pearls.

667
00:36:31,750 --> 00:36:34,230
Among the tribute pearls, there were
12 Qizhen pearls and 12 Babao pearls.

668
00:36:34,790 --> 00:36:36,980
Why is there so much less this year?

669
00:36:40,220 --> 00:36:45,580
[Ledger]

670
00:36:47,840 --> 00:36:50,030
Cui Ding really treats Cui's Pearl Farm

671
00:36:50,030 --> 00:36:51,630
like it's his own,

672
00:36:52,590 --> 00:36:54,670
scheming at every turn.

673
00:36:59,240 --> 00:37:00,150
Master Shijiu,

674
00:37:00,150 --> 00:37:01,590
with so many merchants
attending the pearl auction,

675
00:37:01,960 --> 00:37:04,400
there isn't a dock available right now.

676
00:37:04,720 --> 00:37:06,630
I ask for your patience, sir.

677
00:37:06,630 --> 00:37:07,840
Outrageous!

678
00:37:07,840 --> 00:37:09,440
How dare you make my master wait?

679
00:37:09,440 --> 00:37:10,320
I wouldn't dare,

680
00:37:10,760 --> 00:37:11,360
but...

681
00:37:11,360 --> 00:37:12,400
Just dock.

682
00:37:12,990 --> 00:37:14,590
Dock the ship.

683
00:37:14,590 --> 00:37:16,840
But there are small boats everywhere.

684
00:37:16,840 --> 00:37:19,880
Sink anyone who stands in the way.
I don't care if they live or die.

685
00:37:19,880 --> 00:37:23,670
Get moving. Stop bothering my master.

686
00:37:24,320 --> 00:37:25,590
Why are you still standing here?

687
00:37:25,590 --> 00:37:27,190
Hurry up and do it, now!

688
00:37:49,720 --> 00:37:50,590
Duanwu!

689
00:37:51,510 --> 00:37:53,280
We're safe, Duanwu!

690
00:37:57,800 --> 00:38:00,590
Wake up, Duanwu!

691
00:38:02,240 --> 00:38:03,110
Duanwu?

692
00:38:07,190 --> 00:38:08,150
Hold it here.

693
00:38:08,150 --> 00:38:09,920
Move this finger down.

694
00:38:09,920 --> 00:38:11,470
Yes, grip it tightly here.

695
00:38:11,470 --> 00:38:13,320
Lower your hand a bit.

696
00:38:15,510 --> 00:38:18,030
Sit up straight. Relax your shoulders.

697
00:38:19,320 --> 00:38:20,280
You moved it there again.

698
00:38:20,280 --> 00:38:22,070
You made the same old mistake.

699
00:38:22,070 --> 00:38:24,110
How many times have I told you?
Should you have moved it here?

700
00:38:25,880 --> 00:38:27,150
Three ge from the old stock

701
00:38:27,150 --> 00:38:28,510
plus three ge newly collected.

702
00:38:28,510 --> 00:38:30,070
What's the total?

703
00:38:42,590 --> 00:38:43,960
You are lucky

704
00:38:43,960 --> 00:38:45,070
to come back alive.

705
00:38:45,070 --> 00:38:46,280
Have the medicine.

706
00:38:55,510 --> 00:38:57,510
You must always be fully prepared.

707
00:38:57,510 --> 00:38:58,630
Some things

708
00:38:58,630 --> 00:39:01,070
can be useful when the time is right.

709
00:39:27,720 --> 00:39:28,960
Who sent this?

710
00:39:28,960 --> 00:39:30,960
When we were rushing
to escape the fire,

711
00:39:30,960 --> 00:39:32,320
someone bumped into me.

712
00:39:32,320 --> 00:39:34,110
Later, I found this ledger in my bag.

713
00:39:34,510 --> 00:39:35,630
This ledger

714
00:39:36,030 --> 00:39:38,030
details the pearl farm's harvest,

715
00:39:38,030 --> 00:39:39,800
but it's vastly different
from the tribute pearl records.

716
00:39:40,110 --> 00:39:41,470
What should we do next?

717
00:39:44,590 --> 00:39:45,720
We have material evidence

718
00:39:46,320 --> 00:39:47,400
but no witnesses.

719
00:39:48,920 --> 00:39:49,800
Anyone could've written

720
00:39:49,800 --> 00:39:50,840
these accounts.

721
00:39:51,240 --> 00:39:52,630
Now that the Pearl Tower is destroyed,

722
00:39:52,630 --> 00:39:54,720
the pearl farm could use this opportunity
to cover up their crime.

723
00:39:54,720 --> 00:39:57,960
Cui Ding has probably
figured out your identity, sir.

724
00:39:59,150 --> 00:40:00,280
Who could be pocketing the money

725
00:40:01,630 --> 00:40:03,320
from the private sale of tribute pearls?

726
00:40:03,320 --> 00:40:04,320
I doubt Cui's Pearl Farm

727
00:40:04,320 --> 00:40:05,990
would have the nerve
to commit this crime alone.

728
00:40:07,320 --> 00:40:09,240
Cui Ding is definitely a key player.

729
00:40:10,800 --> 00:40:12,590
Keep a close watch on Cui's Pearl Farm.

730
00:40:12,590 --> 00:40:13,150
Yes, sir.

731
00:40:20,590 --> 00:40:22,320
That ship is heading straight
for the docks,

732
00:40:22,320 --> 00:40:23,470
and there's a small boat in its path.

733
00:40:24,800 --> 00:40:25,840
This is not good.

734
00:40:28,670 --> 00:40:30,190
Duanwu, wake up!

735
00:40:30,190 --> 00:40:31,470
A ship's coming our way!

736
00:40:31,470 --> 00:40:33,800
Stay back! There's a boat here!

737
00:40:33,800 --> 00:40:36,280
Duanwu, wake up!

738
00:40:36,590 --> 00:40:38,470
[Cui]
Don't come any closer!

739
00:40:39,280 --> 00:40:42,110
Stay back!

740
00:40:42,110 --> 00:40:43,360
Duanwu!

741
00:40:43,360 --> 00:40:45,510
Stay away!

742
00:40:48,180 --> 00:40:48,780
[Cui]

743
00:40:51,550 --> 00:40:53,190
Help!

744
00:40:53,630 --> 00:40:54,630
Is anyone there?

745
00:40:54,630 --> 00:40:55,400
Someone's fallen overboard.

746
00:40:55,720 --> 00:40:57,400
- Du Ming, rescue them!

747
00:40:57,400 --> 00:40:57,990
Yes, sir.

748
00:41:28,760 --> 00:41:29,990
Greetings, Lady Shijiu.

749
00:41:29,990 --> 00:41:30,990
Outrageous!

750
00:41:30,990 --> 00:41:33,590
How dare you
keep Master Shijiu waiting this long?

751
00:41:34,590 --> 00:41:36,880
Master Shijiu, welcome to Hepu.

752
00:41:37,510 --> 00:41:38,630
Please forgive me

753
00:41:38,630 --> 00:41:39,720
for being late.

754
00:41:40,280 --> 00:41:42,440
I heard you'd be getting married soon.

755
00:41:42,720 --> 00:41:45,470
Have you come to prepare your dowry?

756
00:41:52,240 --> 00:41:54,400
I see that you're here
on behalf of the master, Master Shijiu.

757
00:41:54,400 --> 00:41:57,470
Are this year's tribute pearls ready?

758
00:41:59,360 --> 00:42:01,280
They were all prepared

759
00:42:01,280 --> 00:42:02,840
and stored in the Pearl Tower.

760
00:42:03,190 --> 00:42:04,880
But there was a terrible fire today,

761
00:42:04,880 --> 00:42:07,400
and now the Pearl Tower
is nothing but rubble.

762
00:42:07,400 --> 00:42:09,110
It was truly a man-made disaster.

763
00:42:09,590 --> 00:42:11,840
There was a defiant slave
on the pearl farm named Duanwu.

764
00:42:11,840 --> 00:42:13,960
She secretly seduced Peng Wu,

765
00:42:13,960 --> 00:42:15,510
and somehow,

766
00:42:15,510 --> 00:42:16,840
she not only killed him

767
00:42:16,840 --> 00:42:17,920
but also colluded with Lady Eight

768
00:42:17,920 --> 00:42:20,190
to burn down the entire Pearl Tower!

769
00:42:20,190 --> 00:42:21,920
May I ask, Steward Cui,

770
00:42:21,920 --> 00:42:23,280
have you caught them?

771
00:42:23,280 --> 00:42:24,150
We're working on it.

772
00:42:25,190 --> 00:42:26,470
Once Duanwu is caught,

773
00:42:26,470 --> 00:42:27,920
everything will come to light.

774
00:42:30,030 --> 00:42:32,110
I don't care about the truth.

775
00:42:33,190 --> 00:42:34,150
Not a single pearl

776
00:42:34,880 --> 00:42:36,320
can be missing.

777
00:42:36,590 --> 00:42:38,760
But how could I possibly
get so many pearls now?

778
00:42:39,070 --> 00:42:41,110
Even if we have to cut you up
and sell the pieces,

779
00:42:41,110 --> 00:42:43,070
the job must be done.

780
00:42:43,070 --> 00:42:44,320
Otherwise,

781
00:42:45,670 --> 00:42:48,280
I'll throw you into the ocean
to feed the sharks.

782
00:42:48,550 --> 00:42:50,280
Would you prefer that, Steward Cui?

783
00:42:52,280 --> 00:42:53,030
Sir,

784
00:42:53,360 --> 00:42:54,920
there's a problem with the gold leaf.

785
00:42:55,400 --> 00:42:56,110
It's fake.

786
00:43:06,440 --> 00:43:07,800
This was left by your father.

787
00:43:07,800 --> 00:43:09,080
Go find him in the Western Regions.

788
00:43:11,380 --> 00:43:12,090
Duanwu,

789
00:43:12,170 --> 00:43:13,060
you're awake!

790
00:43:13,060 --> 00:43:14,250
You finally woke up!

791
00:43:15,900 --> 00:43:17,250
Duanwu, we've made it.

792
00:43:17,250 --> 00:43:18,730
Mr. Zhang saved us.

793
00:43:18,980 --> 00:43:20,610
We're on his ship now.

794
00:43:20,970 --> 00:43:22,200
He said he knew you.

795
00:43:24,570 --> 00:43:25,050
Duanwu,

796
00:43:25,420 --> 00:43:25,900
come on.

797
00:43:27,440 --> 00:43:27,820
Drink this.

798
00:43:29,680 --> 00:43:30,340
By the way, Duanwu,

799
00:43:32,920 --> 00:43:34,320
Lady Eight left this for you.

800
00:43:34,820 --> 00:43:36,460
She was the one who told me
to wait for you by the shore.
